{"_path":"/health/h005","_dir":"health","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"健康體適能飲食","description":null,"image":null,"sequence":5,"category":"飲食健康","link":null,"head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口 - 社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"健康休閒"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-03-27T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"健康體適能飲食"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"健康體適能飲食"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"護理健康計劃-骨質缺乏的護理指導"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"護理健康計劃: 骨質缺乏的護理指導"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"骨骼是活的組織,終其一生,骨頭會持續進行破壞與重建的過程。青少年時期,的重建速度大於破壞速度,屬於骨質增加階段：骨質量持續增加,約在 20~30 歲时達到最高峰,此时的總體骨質量稱為顛峰 質量(peakbonemass),即俗稱的「骨本」此階段約維持 10 ～ 15 年，然後逐漸向下透減。在医學上,這種正常的骨質減少稱為 骨質流失。 但如果骨質減少的速度因為很多因素影響而加快,骨質快速流失之後，骨質疏松症的情形就產生了。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"危險因子:"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"年齡大於 65 歲、女性。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"體重過瘦。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"抽煙、酗酒。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"缺乏運動。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"鈣攝取不足、過量攝取含咖啡因飲料。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"停經後或卵巢切除、早期停經(小於 45 歲)、性荷蒙功能低下等。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"糖尿病、腎臟病、肝病、甲狀腺或副甲狀腺疾病。/li>"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"長期服用類固醇藥物。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"家族病史。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"預防骨質疏鬆症原則:"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"控制體重,維持身體質量指數(BMI)在理想值 18.5 至 24 之間。 (BMI=體重(公斤)/身高(公尺))。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"定期健康檢查:使用雙能量 X 光收儀 (dual-energyX-rayabsorptiometry,DXA 測骨密度,以達到最科學的鑑定。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"規律的生活和運動:這包括了均衡的飲食、早睡早起的習慣、每週固定做三次以上低衝擊性的有氧運動(例如跳繩、慢跑)。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"戒菸,戒酒,減少咖啡攝取。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"飲食衛教計劃:"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"多攝取含豐富鈣質的食物:乳製品(奶粉、乳酪、起司)、海鮮類(小魚乾、蝦米)、類(干、凍豆腐)、深色蔬菜(芥藍菜、紫菜、黑芝麻、金針- 耳、九層塔、髮菜等預防骨質疏鬆。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"避免大量攝取咖啡、酒、茶。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"每天適當的曬太陽接受一些日曬以促進皮膚製造維生素 D。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"可適量服用鈣和維生 D3 補充食品。(最好能先抽血檢測體內血鈣和維生 D 濃度,才清楚需要補充多少單位)"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"補鈣飲食"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n于康说吃 走出补钙误区补钙 最好的时间原来是吃饭中或饭后 饭前补钙不仅无效果还伤胃！"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"健康體適能飲食","depth":2,"text":"健康體適能飲食","children":[{"id":"護理健康計劃-骨質缺乏的護理指導","depth":3,"text":"護理健康計劃: 骨質缺乏的護理指導"}]}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:health:h005.md","_source":"content","_file":"health/h005.md","_extension":"md"}